nowing Winds", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 7, "page": 521, "ruku": 455, "hizb_quarter": 208, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "it", "name": "Piccardo", "transelator_en_name": "Hamza Roberto Piccardo", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4682, "text": "Per il cielo solcato di percorsi,"}, {"id": 372461, "identifier": "it.piccardo", "surah_number": 51, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0630\u0627\u0631\u064a\u0627\u062a", "surah_en_name": "Adh-Dhaariyat", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Winnowing Winds", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 7, "page": 521, "ruku": 455, "hizb_quarter": 208, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "it", "name": "Piccardo", "transelator_en_name": "Hamza Roberto Piccardo", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4683, "text": "invero avete opinioni contrastanti,"}, {"id": 372462, "identifier": "it.piccardo", "surah_number": 51, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0630\u0627\u0631\u064a\u0627\u062a", "surah_en_name": "Adh-Dhaariyat", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Winnowing Winds", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 7, "page": 521, "ruku": 455, "hizb_quarter": 208, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "it", "name": "Piccardo", "transelator_en_name": "Hamza Roberto Piccardo", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4684, "text": "\u00e8 maldisposto chi \u00e8 maldisposto."}, {"id": 372463, "identifier": "it.piccardo", "surah_number": 51, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0630\u0627\u0631\u064a\u0627\u062a", "surah_en_name": "Adh-Dhaariyat", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Winnowing Winds", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 7, "page": 521, "ruku": 455, "hizb_quarter": 208, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "it", "name": "Piccardo", "transelator_en_name": "Hamza Roberto Piccardo", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4685, "text": "Maledetti i blasfemi"}, {"id": 372464, "identifier": "it.piccardo", "surah_number": 51, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0630\u0627\u0631\u064a\u0627\u062a", "surah_en_name": "Adh-Dhaariyat", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Winnowing Winds", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 7, "page": 521, "ruku": 455, "hizb_quarter": 208, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "it", "name": "Piccardo", "transelator_en_name": "Hamza Roberto Piccardo", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4686, "text": "che nell'abisso dimenticano."}, {"id": 372465, "identifier": "it.piccardo", "surah_number": 51, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0630\u0627\u0631\u064a\u0627\u062a", "surah_en_name": "Adh-Dhaariyat", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Winnowing Winds", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 7, "page": 521, "ruku": 455, "hizb_quarter": 208, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "it", "name": "Piccardo", "transelator_en_name": "Hamza Roberto Piccardo", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4687, "text": "Chiedono: \u201cA quando il Giorno del Giudizio?\u201d."}, {"id": 372466, "identifier": "it.piccardo", "surah_number": 51, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0630\u0627\u0631\u064a\u0627\u062a", "surah_en_name": "Adh-Dhaariyat", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Winnowing Winds", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 7, "page": 521, "ruku": 455, "hizb_quarter": 208, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "it", "name": "Piccardo", "transelator_en_name": "Hamza Roberto Piccardo", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4688, "text": "Il Giorno in cui saranno messi alla prova del Fuoco"}, {"id": 372467, "identifier": "it.piccardo", "surah_number": 51, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0630\u0627\u0631\u064a\u0627\u062a", "surah_en_name": "Adh-Dhaariyat", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Winnowing Winds", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 7, "page": 521, "ruku": 455, "hizb_quarter": 208, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "it", "name": "Piccardo", "transelator_en_name": "Hamza Roberto Piccardo", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4689, "text": "[sar\u00e0 detto loro]: \u201cGustate la vostra prova! Ecco quello che volevate affrettare!\u201d."}, {"id": 372468, "identifier": "it.piccardo", "surah_number": 51, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0630\u0627\u0631\u064a\u0627\u062a", "surah_en_name": "Adh-Dhaariyat", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Winnowing Winds", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 7, "page": 521, "ruku": 455, "hizb_quarter": 208, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "it", "name": "Piccardo", "transelator_en_name": "Hamza Roberto Piccardo", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4690, "text": "I timorati staranno tra i giardini e le fonti,"}, {"id": 372469, "identifier": "it.piccardo", "surah_number": 51, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0630\u0627\u0631\u064a\u0627\u062a", "surah_en_name": "Adh-Dhaariyat", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Winnowing Winds", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 7, "page": 521, "ruku": 455, "hizb_quarter": 208, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "it", "name": "Piccardo", "transelator_en_name": "Hamza Roberto Piccardo", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4691, "text": "prendendo ci\u00f2 che il Signore dar\u00e0 loro, poich\u00e9 in passato facevano il bene,"}, {"id": 372470, "identifier": "it.piccardo", "surah_number": 51, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0630\u0627\u0631\u064a\u0627\u062a", "surah_en_name": "Adh-Dhaariyat", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Winnowing Winds", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 7, "page": 521, "ruku": 455, "hizb_quarter": 208, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "it", "name": "Piccardo", "transelator_en_name": "Hamza Roberto Piccardo", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4692, "text": "dormivano poco di notte,"}, {"id": 372471, "identifier": "it.piccardo", "surah_number": 51, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0630\u0627\u0631\u064a\u0627\u062a", "surah_en_name": "Adh-Dhaariyat", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Winnowing Winds", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 7, "page": 521, "ruku": 455, "hizb_quarter": 208, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "it", "name": "Piccardo", "transelator_en_name": "Hamza Roberto Piccardo", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4693, "text": "e all'alba imploravano il perdono;"}, {"id": 372472, "identifier": "it.piccardo", "surah_number": 51, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0630\u0627\u0631\u064a\u0627\u062a", "surah_en_name": "Adh-Dhaariyat", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Winnowing Winds", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 7, "page": 521, "ruku": 455, "hizb_quarter": 208, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "it", "name": "Piccardo", "transelator_en_name": "Hamza Roberto Piccardo", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4694, "text": "e nei loro beni c'era un diritto per il mendicante e il diseredato."}, {"id": 372473, "identifier": "it.piccardo", "surah_number": 51, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0630\u0627\u0631\u064a\u0627\u062a", "surah_en_name": "Adh-Dhaariyat", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Winnowing Winds", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 7, "page": 521, "ruku": 455, "hizb_quarter": 208, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "it", "name": "Piccardo", "transelator_en_name": "Hamza Roberto Piccardo", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4695, "text": "Sulla terra ci sono segni per coloro che credono fermamente,"}, {"id": 372474, "identifier": "it.piccardo", "surah_number": 51, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0630\u0627\u0631\u064a\u0627\u062a", "surah_en_name": "Adh-Dhaariyat", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Winnowing Winds", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 7, "page": 521, "ruku": 455, "hizb_quarter": 208, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "it", "name": "Piccardo", "transelator_en_name": "Hamza Roberto Piccardo", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4696, "text": "e anche in voi stessi. Non riflettete dunque?"}, {"id": 372475, "identifier": "it.piccardo", "surah_number": 51, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0630\u0627\u0631\u064a\u0627\u062a", "surah_en_name": "Adh-Dhaariyat", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Winnowing Winds", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 7, "page": 521, "ruku": 455, "hizb_quarter": 208, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "it", "name": "Piccardo", "transelator_en_name": "Hamza Roberto Piccardo", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4697, "text": "Nel cielo c'\u00e8 la vostra sussistenza e anche ci\u00f2 che vi \u00e8 stato promesso."}, {"id": 372476, "identifier": "it.piccardo", "surah_number": 51, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0630\u0627\u0631\u064a\u0627\u062a", "surah_en_name": "Adh-Dhaariyat", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Winnowing Winds", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 7, "page": 521, "ruku": 455, "hizb_quarter": 208, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "it", "name": "Piccardo", "transelator_en_name": "Hamza Roberto Piccardo", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4698, "text": "Per il Signore del cielo e della terra: tutto questo \u00e8 vero come \u00e8 vero che parlate."}, {"id": 372477, "identifier": "it.piccardo", "surah_number": 51, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0630\u0627\u0631\u064a\u0627\u062a", "surah_en_name": "Adh-Dhaariyat", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Winnowing Winds", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 7, "page": 521, "ruku": 456, "hizb_quarter": 208, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "it", "name": "Piccardo", "transelator_en_name": "Hamza Roberto Piccardo", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4699, "text": "Ti \u00e8 giunta la storia degli ospiti onorati di Abramo ?"}, {"id": 372478, "identifier": "it.piccardo", "surah_number": 51, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0630\u0627\u0631\u064a\u0627\u062a", "surah_en_name": "Adh-Dhaariyat", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Winnowing Winds", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 7, "page": 521, "ruku": 456, "hizb_quarter": 208, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "it", "name": "Piccardo", "transelator_en_name": "Hamza Roberto Piccardo", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4700, "text": "Quando entrarono da lui dicendo: \u201cPace\u201d, egli rispose: \u201cPace, o sconosciuti\u201d."}, {"id": 372479, "identifier": "it.piccardo", "surah_number": 51, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0630\u0627\u0631\u064a\u0627\u062a", "surah_en_name": "Adh-Dhaariyat", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Winnowing Winds", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 7, "page": 521, "ruku": 456, "hizb_quarter": 208, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "it", "name": "Piccardo", "transelator_en_name": "Hamza Roberto Piccardo", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4701, "text": "Poi and\u00f2 discretamente dai suoi e torn\u00f2 con un vitello grasso,"}, {"id": 372480, "identifier": "it.piccardo", "surah_number": 51, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0630\u0627\u0631\u064a\u0627\u062a", "surah_en_name": "Adh-Dhaariyat", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Winnowing Winds", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 7, "page": 521, "ruku": 456, "hizb_quarter": 208, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "it", "name": "Piccardo", "transelator_en_name": "Hamza Roberto Piccardo", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4702, "text": "e l'offr\u00ec loro... [Disse]: \u201cNon mangiate nulla?\u201d."}, {"id": 372481, "identifier": "it.piccardo", "surah_number": 51, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0630\u0627\u0631\u064a\u0627\u062a", "surah_en_name": "Adh-Dhaariyat", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Winnowing Winds", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 7, "page": 521, "ruku": 456, "hizb_quarter": 208, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "it", "name": "Piccardo", "transelator_en_name": "Hamza Roberto Piccardo", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4703, "text": "Ebbe allora paura di loro. Dissero: \u201cNon aver paura\u201d. Gli diedero la lieta novella di un figlio sapiente."}, {"id": 372482, "identifier": "it.piccardo", "surah_number": 51, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0630\u0627\u0631\u064a\u0627\u062a", "surah_en_name": "Adh-Dhaariyat", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Winnowing Winds", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 7, "page": 521, "ruku": 456, "hizb_quarter": 208, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "it", "name": "Piccardo", "transelator_en_name": "Hamza Roberto Piccardo", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4704, "text": "Venne dunque sua moglie gridando, colpendosi il volto e dicendo: \u201cSono una vecchia sterile!\u201d."}, {"id": 372483, "identifier": "it.piccardo", "surah_number": 51, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0630\u0627\u0631\u064a\u0627\u062a", "surah_en_name": "Adh-Dhaariyat", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Winnowing Winds", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 7, "page": 521, "ruku": 456, "hizb_quarter": 208, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "it", "name": "Piccardo", "transelator_en_name": "Hamza Roberto Piccardo", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4705, "text": "Dissero: \u201cCos\u00ec ha comandato il tuo Signore. In verit\u00e0 Egli \u00e8 il Saggio, il Sapiente\u201d."}, {"id": 372484, "identifier": "it.piccardo", "surah_number": 51, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0630\u0627\u0631\u064a\u0627\u062a", "surah_en_name": "Adh-Dhaariyat", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Winnowing Winds", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 27, "manzil": 7, "page": 522, "ruku": 456, "hizb_quarter": 209, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "it", "name": "Piccardo", "transelator_en_name": "Hamza Roberto Piccardo", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4706, "text": "Disse [Abramo]: \u201cO inviati, qual \u00e8 la vostra missione?\u201d."}, {"id": 372485, "identifier": "it.piccardo", "surah_number": 51, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0630\u0627\u0631\u064a\u0627\u062a", "surah_en_name": "Adh-Dhaariyat", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Winnowing Winds", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 27, "manzil": 7, "page": 522, "ruku": 456, "hizb_quarter": 209, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "it", "name": "Piccardo", "transelator_en_name": "Hamza Roberto Piccardo", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4707, "text": "Risposero: \u201cSiamo stati inviati a un popolo di criminali,"}, {"id": 372487, "identifier": "it.piccardo", "surah_number": 51, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0630\u0627\u0631\u064a\u0627\u062a", "surah_en_name": "Adh-Dhaariyat", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Winnowing Winds", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 27, "manzil": 7, "page": 522, "ruku": 456, "hizb_quarter": 209, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "it", "name": "Piccardo", "transelator_en_name": "Hamza Roberto Piccardo", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4708, "text": "per lanciare su di loro pietre d'argilla"}, {"id": 372488, "identifier": "it.piccardo", "surah_number": 51, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0630\u0627\u0631\u064a\u0627\u062a", "surah_en_name": "Adh-Dhaariyat", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Winnowing Winds", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 27, "manzil": 7, "page": 522, "ruku": 456, "hizb_quarter": 209, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "it", "name": "Piccardo", "transelator_en_name": "Hamza Roberto Piccardo", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4709, "text": "contrassegnate presso il tuo Signore, per coloro che eccedono\u201d."}, {"id": 372489, "identifier": "it.piccardo", "surah_number": 51, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0630\u0627\u0631\u064a\u0627\u062a", "surah_en_name": "Adh-Dhaariyat", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Winnowing Winds", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 27, "manzil": 7, "page": 522, "ruku": 456, "hizb_quarter": 209, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "it", "name": "Piccardo", "transelator_en_name": "Hamza Roberto Piccardo", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4710, "text": "Ne facemmo uscire i credenti"}, {"id": 372490, "identifier": "it.piccardo", "surah_number": 51, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0630\u0627\u0631\u064a\u0627\u062a", "surah_en_name": "Adh-Dhaariyat", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Winnowing Winds", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 27, "manzil": 7, "page": 522, "ruku": 456, "hizb_quarter": 209, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "it", "name": "Piccardo", "transelator_en_name": "Hamza Roberto Piccardo", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4711, "text": "e non vi trovammo che una casa di sottomessi."}, {"id": 372491, "identifier": "it.piccardo", "surah_number": 51, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0630\u0627\u0631\u064a\u0627\u062a", "surah_en_name": "Adh-Dhaariyat", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Winnowing Winds", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 27, "manzil": 7, "page": 522, "ruku": 456, "hizb_quarter": 209, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "it", "name": "Piccardo", "transelator_en_name": "Hamza Roberto Piccardo", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4712, "text": "Col\u00e0 lasciammo un segno per coloro che temono il castigo doloroso;"}, {"id": 372492, "identifier": "it.piccardo", "surah_number": 51, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0630\u0627\u0631\u064a\u0627\u062a", "surah_en_name": "Adh-Dhaariyat", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Winnowing Winds", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 27, "manzil": 7, "page": 522, "ruku": 456, "hizb_quarter": 209, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "it", "name": "Piccardo", "transelator_en_name": "Hamza Roberto Piccardo", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4713, "text": "come in Mos\u00e8, quando lo inviammo a Faraone con autorit\u00e0 incontestabile,"}, {"id": 372493, "identifier": "it.piccardo", "surah_number": 51, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0630\u0627\u0631\u064a\u0627\u062a", "surah_en_name": "Adh-Dhaariyat", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Winnowing Winds", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 27, "manzil": 7, "page": 522, "ruku": 456, "hizb_quarter": 209, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "it", "name": "Piccardo", "transelator_en_name": "Hamza Roberto Piccardo", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4714, "text": "ma volse le spalle insieme coi suoi. Disse: \u201c\u00c8 uno stregone o un posseduto\u201d."}, {"id": 372494, "identifier": "it.piccardo", "surah_number": 51, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0630\u0627\u0631\u064a\u0627\u062a", "surah_en_name": "Adh-Dhaariyat", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Winnowing Winds", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 27, "manzil": 7, "page": 522, "ruku": 456, "hizb_quarter": 209, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "it", "name": "Piccardo", "transelator_en_name": "Hamza Roberto Piccardo", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4715, "text": "Afferrammo lui e le sue truppe e li gettammo nei flutti, per il suo comportamento biasimevole."}, {"id": 372495, "identifier": "it.piccardo", "surah_number": 51, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0630\u0627\u0631\u064a\u0627\u062a", "surah_en_name": "Adh-Dhaariyat", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Winnowing Winds", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 27, "manzil": 7, "page": 522, "ruku": 456, "hizb_quarter": 209, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "it", "name": "Piccardo", "transelator_en_name": "Hamza Roberto Piccardo", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4716, "text": "E [ci fu segno] negli \u0091\u00c2d, quando inviammo contro di loro il vento devastante"}, {"id": 372496, "identifier": "it.piccardo", "surah_number": 51, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0630\u0627\u0631\u064a\u0627\u062a", "surah_en_name": "Adh-Dhaariyat", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Winnowing Winds", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 27, "manzil": 7, "page": 522, "ruku": 456, "hizb_quarter": 209, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "it", "name": "Piccardo", "transelator_en_name": "Hamza Roberto Piccardo", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4717, "text": "che nulla lasciava sul suo percorso senza ridurlo in polvere."}, {"id": 372497, "identifier": "it.piccardo", "surah_number": 51, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0630\u0627\u0631\u064a\u0627\u062a", "surah_en_name": "Adh-Dhaariyat", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Winnowing Winds", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 27, "manzil": 7, "page": 522, "ruku": 456, "hizb_quarter": 209, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "it", "name": "Piccardo", "transelator_en_name": "Hamza Roberto Piccardo", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4718, "text": "E [ci fu segno] nei Tham\u00fbd, quando fu detto loro: \u201cGodete per un periodo\u201d."}, {"id": 372498, "identifier": "it.piccardo", "surah_number": 51, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0630\u0627\u0631\u064a\u0627\u062a", "surah_en_name": "Adh-Dhaariyat", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Winnowing Winds", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 27, "manzil": 7, "page": 522, "ruku": 456, "hizb_quarter": 209, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "it", "name": "Piccardo", "transelator_en_name": "Hamza Roberto Piccardo", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4719, "text": "Trasgredirono l'ordine del loro Signore. Li colp\u00ec una folgore mentre ancora guardavano,"}, {"id": 372499, "identifier": "it.piccardo", "surah_number": 51, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0630\u0627\u0631\u064a\u0627\u062a", "surah_en_name": "Adh-Dhaariyat", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Winnowing Winds", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 27, "manzil": 7, "page": 522, "ruku": 456, "hizb_quarter": 209, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "it", "name": "Piccardo", "transelator_en_name": "Hamza Roberto Piccardo", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4720, "text": "e non poterono restare in piedi n\u00e9 essere soccorsi."}, {"id": 372500, "identifier": "it.piccardo", "surah_number": 51, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0630\u0627\u0631\u064a\u0627\u062a", "surah_en_name": "Adh-Dhaariyat", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Winnowing Winds", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 27, "manzil": 7, "page": 522, "ruku": 456, "hizb_quarter": 209, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "it", "name": "Piccardo", "transelator_en_name": "Hamza Roberto Piccardo", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4721, "text": "Gi\u00e0 [distruggemmo] il popolo di No\u00e8: erano gente malvagia."}, {"id": 372501, "identifier": "it.piccardo", "surah_number": 51, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0630\u0627\u0631\u064a\u0627\u062a", "surah_en_name": "Adh-Dhaariyat", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Winnowing Winds", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 27, "manzil": 7, "page": 522, "ruku": 457, "hizb_quarter": 209, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "it", "name": "Piccardo", "transelator_en_name": "Hamza Roberto Piccardo", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4722, "text": "Il cielo lo abbiamo costruito con la Nostra potenza e [costantemente] lo estendiamo nell'immensit\u00e0;"}, {"id": 372502, "identifier": "it.piccardo", "surah_number": 51, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0630\u0627\u0631\u064a\u0627\u062a", "surah_en_name": "Adh-Dhaariyat", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Winnowing Winds", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 27, "manzil": 7, "page": 522, "ruku": 457, "hizb_quarter": 209, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "it", "name": "Piccardo", "transelator_en_name": "Hamza Roberto Piccardo", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4723, "text": "la terra l'abbiamo distesa, e quanto bene la distendemmo !"}, {"id": 372503, "identifier": "it.piccardo", "surah_number": 51, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0630\u0627\u0631\u064a\u0627\u062a", "surah_en_name": "Adh-Dhaariyat", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Winnowing Winds", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 27, "manzil": 7, "page": 522, "ruku": 457, "hizb_quarter": 209, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "it", "name": "Piccardo", "transelator_en_name": "Hamza Roberto Piccardo", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4724, "text": "Di ogni cosa creammo una coppia, affinch\u00e9 possiate riflettere."}, {"id": 372504, "identifier": "it.piccardo", "surah_number": 51, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0630\u0627\u0631\u064a\u0627\u062a", "surah_en_name": "Adh-Dhaariyat", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Winnowing Winds", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 27, "manzil": 7, "page": 522, "ruku": 457, "hizb_quarter": 209, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "it", "name": "Piccardo", "transelator_en_name": "Hamza Roberto Piccardo", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4725, "text": "\u201cAccorrete allora verso Allah! In verit\u00e0 io sono per voi un ammonitore esplicito da parte Sua."}, {"id": 372505, "identifier": "it.piccardo", "surah_number": 51, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0630\u0627\u0631\u064a\u0627\u062a", "surah_en_name": "Adh-Dhaariyat", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Winnowing Winds", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 27, "manzil": 7, "page": 522, "ruku": 457, "hizb_quarter": 209, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "it", "name": "Piccardo", "transelator_en_name": "Hamza Roberto Piccardo", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4726, "text": "Non associate altra divinit\u00e0 ad Allah. In verit\u00e0 io sono per voi un ammonitore esplicito da parte Sua.\u201d"}, {"id": 372506, "identifier": "it.piccardo", "surah_number": 51, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0630\u0627\u0631\u064a\u0627\u062a", "surah_en_name": "Adh-Dhaariyat", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Winnowing Winds", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 27, "manzil": 7, "page": 523, "ruku": 457, "hizb_quarter": 209, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "it", "name": "Piccardo", "transelator_en_name": "Hamza Roberto Piccardo", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4727, "text": "Non mai giunse un messaggero a quelli che li precedettero senza che gli dicessero: \u201cSei uno stregone, un pazzo!\u201d."}, {"id": 372507, "identifier": "it.piccardo", "surah_number": 51, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0630\u0627\u0631\u064a\u0627\u062a", "surah_en_name": "Adh-Dhaariyat", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Winnowing Winds", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 27, "manzil": 7, "page": 523, "ruku": 457, "hizb_quarter": 209, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "it", "name": "Piccardo", "transelator_en_name": "Hamza Roberto Piccardo", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4728, "text": "\u00c8 questo quel che si sono tramandati ? \u00c8 davvero gente ribelle."}, {"id": 372508, "identifier": "it.piccardo", "surah_number": 51, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0630\u0627\u0631\u064a\u0627\u062a", "surah_en_name": "Adh-Dhaariyat", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Winnowing Winds", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 27, "manzil": 7, "page": 523, "ruku": 457, "hizb_quarter": 209, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "it", "name": "Piccardo", "transelator_en_name": "Hamza Roberto Piccardo", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4729, "text": "Volgi loro le spalle: non sarai biasimato ;"}, {"id": 372509, "identifier": "it.piccardo", "surah_number": 51, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0630\u0627\u0631\u064a\u0627\u062a", "surah_en_name": "Adh-Dhaariyat", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Winnowing Winds", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 27, "manzil": 7, "page": 523, "ruku": 457, "hizb_quarter": 209, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "it", "name": "Piccardo", "transelator_en_name": "Hamza Roberto Piccardo", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4730, "text": "e ricorda, ch\u00e9 il ricordo giova ai credenti."}, {"id": 372510, "identifier": "it.piccardo", "surah_number": 51, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0630\u0627\u0631\u064a\u0627\u062a", "surah_en_name": "Adh-Dhaariyat", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Winnowing Winds", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 27, "manzil": 7, "page": 523, "ruku": 457, "hizb_quarter": 209, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "it", "name": "Piccardo", "transelator_en_name": "Hamza Roberto Piccardo", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4731, "text": "\u00c8 solo perch\u00e9 Mi adorassero che ho creato i d\u00e8moni e gli uomini."}, {"id": 372511, "identifier": "it.piccardo", "surah_number": 51, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0630\u0627\u0631\u064a\u0627\u062a", "surah_en_name": "Adh-Dhaariyat", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Winnowing Winds", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 27, "manzil": 7, "page": 523, "ruku": 457, "hizb_quarter": 209, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "it", "name": "Piccardo", "transelator_en_name": "Hamza Roberto Piccardo", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4732, "text": "Non chiedo loro nessun sostentamento e non chiedo che Mi nutrano."}, {"id": 372512, "identifier": "it.piccardo", "surah_number": 51, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0630\u0627\u0631\u064a\u0627\u062a", "surah_en_name": "Adh-Dhaariyat", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Winnowing Winds", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 27, "manzil": 7, "page": 523, "ruku": 457, "hizb_quarter": 209, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "it", "name": "Piccardo", "transelator_en_name": "Hamza Roberto Piccardo", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4733, "text": "In verit\u00e0 Allah \u00e8 il Sostentatore, il Detentore della forza, l'Irremovibile."}, {"id": 372513, "identifier": "it.piccardo", "surah_number": 51, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0630\u0627\u0631\u064a\u0627\u062a", "surah_en_name": "Adh-Dhaariyat", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Winnowing Winds", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 27, "manzil": 7, "page": 523, "ruku": 457, "hizb_quarter": 209, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "it", "name": "Piccardo", "transelator_en_name": "Hamza Roberto Piccardo", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4734, "text": "Coloro che saranno stati ingiusti avranno la stessa sorte che tocc\u00f2 ai loro simili: non cerchino quindi di affrettarla."}, {"id": 372514, "identifier": "it.piccardo", "surah_number": 51, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0630\u0627\u0631\u064a\u0627\u062a", "surah_en_name": "Adh-Dhaariyat", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Winnowing Winds", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 27, "manzil": 7, "page": 523, "ruku": 457, "hizb_quarter": 209, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "it", "name": "Piccardo", "transelator_en_name": "Hamza Roberto Piccardo", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4735, "text": "Guai a coloro che non credono, per via del Giorno di cui sono stati minacciati."}]